534 
535 bool NPEffectiveGIMR::PostUpdate()
536 {
537  if (!NPbase::PostUpdate()) return (false);
538 
539  LambdaNP2 = Lambda_NP * Lambda_NP;
540  v2_over_LambdaNP2 = v() * v() / LambdaNP2;
541  if (FlagMwInput)
542  cW_tree = MwInput / Mz;
543  else
544  cW_tree = Mw_tree() / Mz;
545  cW2_tree = cW_tree * cW_tree;
546  sW2_tree = 1.0 - cW2_tree;
547  sW_tree = sqrt(sW2_tree);
548 
549  delta_ZZ = (cW2_tree * CHW + sW2_tree * CHB + sW_tree * cW_tree * CHWB) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
550  delta_AA = (sW2_tree * CHW + cW2_tree * CHB - sW_tree * cW_tree * CHWB) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
551  delta_AZ = 2.0 * sW_tree * cW_tree * (CHW - CHB) * v2_over_LambdaNP2
552  - (cW2_tree - sW2_tree) * CHWB * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
553  delta_h = (-CHD / 4.0 + CHbox) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
554 
555  return (true);
556 }

1444 bool NPEffectiveGIMR::CheckParameters(const std::map<std::string, double>& DPars)
1445 {
1446  if (FlagLeptonUniversal && FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1447  if (FlagMwInput) {
1448  if (DPars.find("MwInput") == DPars.end()) {
1449  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMR_LFU_QFU parameter MwInput" << std::endl;
1450  return false;
1451  }
1452  }
1453  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRVars_LFU_QFU; i++) {
1454  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRVars_LFU_QFU[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1455  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMR_LFU_QFU parameter "
1456  << NPEffectiveGIMRVars_LFU_QFU[i] << std::endl;
1457  return false;
1458  }
1459  }
1460  //} else if (FlagLeptonUniversal && !FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1461  //} else if (!FlagLeptonUniversal && FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1462  } else if (!FlagLeptonUniversal && !FlagQuarkUniversal) {
1463  if (FlagMwInput) {
1464  if (DPars.find("MwInput") == DPars.end()) {
1465  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMR parameter MwInput" << std::endl;
1466  return false;
1467  }
1468  }
1469  for (int i = 0; i < NNPEffectiveGIMRVars; i++) {
1470  if (DPars.find(NPEffectiveGIMRVars[i]) == DPars.end()) {
1471  std::cout << "ERROR: Missing mandatory NPEffectiveGIMR parameter"
1472  << NPEffectiveGIMRVars[i] << std::endl;
1473  return false;
1474  }
1475  }
1476  } else
1477  throw std::runtime_error("Error in NPEffectiveGIMR::CheckParameters()");
1478 
1479  return (NPbase::CheckParameters(DPars));
1480 }
1481 
1482 bool NPEffectiveGIMR::setFlag(const std::string name, const bool value)
1483 {
1484  bool res = false;
1485  if (name.compare("MwInput") == 0) {
1486  FlagMwInput = value;
1487  res = true;
1488  } else if (name.compare("QuadraticTerms") == 0) {
1489  FlagQuadraticTerms = value;
1490  if(value) setModelLinearized(false);
1491  res = true;
1492  } else
1493  res = NPbase::setFlag(name, value);
1494 
1495  return (res);
1496 }

1687  return ((CHL3_11 + CHL3_22 - 0.5 * (CLL_1221 + CLL_2112)) * v2_over_LambdaNP2);
1688 }

1691 {
1692  return (4.0 * sW_tree * cW_tree * CHWB / alphaMz() * v2_over_LambdaNP2);
1693 }

1705 double NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaMz2() const
1706 {
1707  return (2.0*(cW2_tree*CHW+sW2_tree*CHB+cW_tree*sW_tree*CHWB)*v2_over_LambdaNP2);
1708 }

1710 double NPEffectiveGIMR::Mw() const
1711 {
1712  if (FlagMwInput)
1713  return MwInput;
1714  else
1715  return (trueSM.Mw() - Mw_tree() / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1716  *(4.0 * sW_tree * cW_tree * CHWB * v2_over_LambdaNP2
1717  + cW2_tree * CHD * v2_over_LambdaNP2
1718  + 2.0 * sW2_tree * DeltaGF()));
1719 }
1720 
1721 double NPEffectiveGIMR::GammaW() const
1722 {
1723  double G0 = GF * pow(Mw(), 3.0) / 6.0 / sqrt(2.0) / M_PI;
1724  double GammaW_tree = (3.0 + 2.0 * Nc) * G0;
1725 
1726  if (FlagMwInput)
1727  throw std::runtime_error("Write codes in NPEffectiveGIMR::GammaW()!");
1728  else
1729  return (trueSM.GammaW()
1730  - 3.0 * GammaW_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1731  *(4.0 * sW_tree * cW_tree * CHWB * v2_over_LambdaNP2
1732  + cW2_tree * CHD * v2_over_LambdaNP2
1733  + 2.0 * (1.0 + cW2_tree) / 3.0 * DeltaGF())
1734  + 2.0 * GammaW_tree / 3.0 * (CHL3_11 + CHQ3_11 + CHQ3_22) * v2_over_LambdaNP2);
1735 }

1737 double NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGV_f(const Particle p) const
1738 {
1739  return (deltaGL_f(p) + deltaGR_f(p));
1740 }
1741 
1742 double NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGA_f(const Particle p) const
1743 {
1744  return (deltaGL_f(p) - deltaGR_f(p));
1745 }
1746 
1747 double NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGL_f(const Particle p) const
1748 {
1749  double I3p = p.getIsospin(), Qp = p.getCharge();
1750  double CHF1 = CHF1_diag(p);
1751  double CHF3 = CHF3_diag(p);
1752  double NPindirect;
1753  if (FlagMwInput) {
1754  NPindirect = -I3p / 4.0 * (CHD * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 2.0 * DeltaGF())
1755  + Qp * sW2_tree
1756  * ((cW_tree / sW_tree * CHWB + (1.0 + cW2_tree) / 4.0 / sW2_tree * CHD) * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 0.5 * DeltaGF());
1757  } else {
1758  NPindirect = -I3p / 4.0 * (CHD * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 2.0 * DeltaGF())
1759  - Qp * sW2_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1760  *((4.0 * cW_tree / sW_tree * CHWB + CHD) * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 2.0 * DeltaGF());
1761  }
1762  double NPdirect = -0.5 * (CHF1 - 2.0 * I3p * CHF3) * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
1763  return (NPindirect + NPdirect);
1764 }
1765 
1766 double NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGR_f(const Particle p) const
1767 {
1768  double Qp = p.getCharge();
1769  double CHf = CHf_diag(p);
1770  double NPindirect;
1771  if (FlagMwInput) {
1772  NPindirect = Qp * sW2_tree
1773  * ((cW_tree / sW_tree * CHWB + (1.0 + cW2_tree) / 4.0 / sW2_tree * CHD) * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 0.5 * DeltaGF());
1774  } else {
1775  NPindirect = -Qp * sW2_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1776  *((4.0 * cW_tree / sW_tree * CHWB + CHD) * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 2.0 * DeltaGF());
1777  }
1778  double NPdirect = -0.5 * CHf*v2_over_LambdaNP2;
1779  return (NPindirect + NPdirect);
1780 }

1785 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGL_Wff(const Particle pbar, const Particle p) const
1786 {
1787  if (pbar.getIndex() + 1 != p.getIndex() || pbar.getIndex() % 2 != 0)
1788  throw std::runtime_error("NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaGL_Wff(): Not implemented");
1789 
1790  double CHF3 = CHF3_diag(pbar);
1791  double NPindirect;
1792  if (FlagMwInput) {
1793  NPindirect = -0.5 * DeltaGF();
1794  } else {
1795  NPindirect = -cW2_tree / 4.0 / (cW2_tree - sW2_tree)
1796  * ((4.0 * sW_tree / cW_tree * CHWB + CHD) * v2_over_LambdaNP2 + 2.0 * DeltaGF());
1797  }
1798  double NPdirect = CHF3 * v2_over_LambdaNP2;
1799  return (NPindirect + NPdirect);
1800 }

1871 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMR::deltaG_hff(const Particle p) const
1872 {
1873  /* The effects of the RG running are neglected. */
1874  double mf;
1875  if (p.is("TOP"))
1876  //mf = p.getMass(); // m_t(m_t)
1877  mf = mtpole; // pole mass
1878  else
1879  mf = p.getMass();
1880  gslpp::complex CfH = CfH_diag(p);
1881  return (-mf / v() * (delta_h - 0.5 * DeltaGF())
1882  + CfH * v2_over_LambdaNP2 / sqrt(2.0));
1883 }

1968 
1969 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMR::f_triangle(const double tau) const
1970 {
1971  gslpp::complex tmp;
1972  if (tau >= 1.0) {
1973  tmp = asin(1.0 / sqrt(tau));
1974  return (tmp * tmp);
1975  } else {
1976  tmp = log((1.0 + sqrt(1.0 - tau)) / (1.0 - sqrt(1.0 - tau))) - M_PI * gslpp::complex::i();
1977  return (-0.25 * tmp * tmp);
1978  }
1979 }
1980 
1981 gslpp::complex NPEffectiveGIMR::AH_f(const double tau) const
1982 {
1983  return (2.0 * tau * (1.0 + (1.0 - tau) * f_triangle(tau)));
1984 }

1986 double NPEffectiveGIMR::muggH(const double sqrt_s) const
1987 {
1988  double m_t = mtpole;
1989  //doulbe m_t = quarks[TOP].getMass();
1990  //double m_b = quarks[BOTTOM].getMass();
1991 
1992  gslpp::complex dKappa_t = deltaG_hff(quarks[TOP]) / (-m_t / v());
1993  //gslpp::complex dKappa_b = deltaG_hff(quarks[BOTTOM]) / (-m_b / v());
1994 
1995  /* L_eff = G_eff_t_SM*hGG */
1996  gslpp::complex G_eff_t_SM = AlsMz / 16.0 / M_PI / v() * AH_f(4.0 * m_t * m_t / mHl / mHl);
1997 
1998  //double sigma_tt_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_tt(sqrt_s);
1999  //double sigma_bb_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_bb(sqrt_s);
2000  //double sigma_tb_SM = trueSM.computeSigmaggH_tb(sqrt_s);
2001  //gslpp::complex tmp = (2.0 * dKappa_t * sigma_tt_SM
2002  // + 2.0 * dKappa_b * sigma_bb_SM
2003  // + (dKappa_t + dKappa_b) * sigma_tb_SM)
2004  // / (sigma_tt_SM + sigma_bb_SM + sigma_tb_SM);
2005  gslpp::complex tmp = CHG / v() * v2_over_LambdaNP2 / G_eff_t_SM;
2006 
2007  double mu = (1.0 + 2.0 * ( dKappa_t.real() + tmp.real() ) );
2008 
2009  if (FlagQuadraticTerms) {
2010  //Add contributions that are quadratic in the effective coefficients
2011  gslpp::complex tmp2 = dKappa_t + tmp;
2012 
2013  mu += tmp2.abs2();
2014 
2015  }
2016 
2017  if (mu < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
2018 
2019  return mu;
2020 }

2668 double NPEffectiveGIMR::muVH(const double sqrt_s) const
2669 {

2671  double sigmaZH_SM = computeSigmaZH(sqrt_s);

2673  double sigmaZH = muZH(sqrt_s) * sigmaZH_SM;
2674  double mu = ((sigmaWH + sigmaZH) / (sigmaWH_SM + sigmaZH_SM));
2675 
2676  if (mu < 0) return std::numeric_limits<double>::quiet_NaN();
2677 
2678  return mu;

3638  deltaGL_f(quarks[BOTTOM]),
3639  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3640  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3641  deltaMz2()};
3642  sigma = trueSM.LEP2sigmaBottom(s);
3643  dFminusB = myLEP2GIMR.sigmaFminusB_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::quark(BOTTOM), s, GIMRParam);
3644 
3645  AFB_bottom = trueSM.LEP2AFBbottom(s) * (1. - myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::quark(BOTTOM), s, GIMRParam) / sigma)
3646  + dFminusB / sigma;
3647 
3648  return AFB_bottom;
3649 }

3652 double NPEffectiveGIMR::LEP2Rcharm(const double s) const
3653 {
3654  double R_charm = 0., dsigma_c = 0.0, dsigma_had =0.0, sigma_hSM = 0.0;
3655  double GIMRParamUP[10] = {CLL_up(), CLR_up(), CRL_up(), CRR_up(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3656  deltaGR_f(quarks[UP]),
3657  deltaGL_f(quarks[UP]),
3658  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3659  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3660  deltaMz2()};
3661 
3662  double GIMRParamDOWN[10] = {CLL_down(), CLR_down(), CRL_down(), CRR_down(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3663  deltaGR_f(quarks[DOWN]),
3664  deltaGL_f(quarks[DOWN]),
3665  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3666  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3667  deltaMz2()};
3668 
3669  double GIMRParamSTRANGE[10] = {CLL_strange(), CLR_strange(), CRL_strange(), CRR_strange(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3670  deltaGR_f(quarks[STRANGE]),
3671  deltaGL_f(quarks[STRANGE]),
3672  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3673  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3674  deltaMz2()};
3675 
3676  double GIMRParamCHARM[10] = {CLL_charm(), CLR_charm(), CRL_charm(), CRR_charm(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3677  deltaGR_f(quarks[CHARM]),
3678  deltaGL_f(quarks[CHARM]),
3679  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3680  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3681  deltaMz2()};
3682 
3683  double GIMRParamBOTTOM[10] = {CLL_bottom(), CLR_bottom(), CRL_bottom(), CRR_bottom(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3684  deltaGR_f(quarks[BOTTOM]),
3685  deltaGL_f(quarks[BOTTOM]),
3686  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3687  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3688  deltaMz2()};
3689 
3690  sigma_hSM = trueSM.LEP2sigmaHadron(s);
3691 
3692  dsigma_had = myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::UP, s, GIMRParamUP) +
3693  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::DOWN, s, GIMRParamDOWN) +
3694  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::CHARM, s, GIMRParamCHARM) +
3695  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::STRANGE, s, GIMRParamSTRANGE) +
3696  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::BOTTOM, s, GIMRParamBOTTOM);
3697 
3698  dsigma_c = myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::CHARM, s, GIMRParamCHARM);
3699 
3700  R_charm = trueSM.LEP2Rcharm(s) * (1 - dsigma_had / sigma_hSM) + dsigma_c / sigma_hSM;
3701 
3702  return R_charm;
3703 }

3705 double NPEffectiveGIMR::LEP2Rbottom(const double s) const
3706 {
3707  double R_bottom = 0., dsigma_b = 0.0, dsigma_had =0.0, sigma_hSM = 0.0;
3708  double GIMRParamUP[10] = {CLL_up(), CLR_up(), CRL_up(), CRR_up(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3709  deltaGR_f(quarks[UP]),
3710  deltaGL_f(quarks[UP]),

3713  deltaMz2()};
3714

3716  deltaGR_f(quarks[DOWN]),
3717  deltaGL_f(quarks[DOWN]),
3718  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3719  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3720  deltaMz2()};
3721

3723  deltaGR_f(quarks[STRANGE]),
3724  deltaGL_f(quarks[STRANGE]),
3725  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3726  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3727  deltaMz2()};
3728 
3729  double GIMRParamCHARM[10] = {CLL_charm(), CLR_charm(), CRL_charm(), CRR_charm(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3730  deltaGR_f(quarks[CHARM]),
3731  deltaGL_f(quarks[CHARM]),
3732  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3733  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3734  deltaMz2()};
3735 
3736  double GIMRParamBOTTOM[10] = {CLL_bottom(), CLR_bottom(), CRL_bottom(), CRR_bottom(), deltaGamma_Z(),
3737  deltaGR_f(quarks[BOTTOM]),
3738  deltaGL_f(quarks[BOTTOM]),
3739  deltaGR_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3740  deltaGL_f(leptons[ELECTRON]),
3741  deltaMz2()};

3744

3746  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::DOWN, s, GIMRParamDOWN) +

3748  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::STRANGE, s, GIMRParamSTRANGE) +
3749  myLEP2GIMR.sigma_q_LEP2_GIMR(QCD::BOTTOM, s, GIMRParamBOTTOM);
3750

3752
